  "meal_prep_notes": "Upma keeps 2 days refrigerated. Reheat in a covered pan with 2 tbsp water over low heat for 3 minutes to restore softness. For batch cooking, roast the grain and portion the tempering ingredients ahead so breakfast comes together quickly.",
